  "decision_conditions": [
    "REASON: The proposed roof extension by virtue of its design, scale, and massing would dominate the rear roof space and therefore represent an unsightly interruption from the existing continuous uniform and rhythmic rear roofslopes along the terrace row from 186- 200 Tufnell Park Road. The proposed development would form a discordant rear feature and is therefore considered to be contrary to Policies to D1 (Urban Context), D4 (Designing in context), D11 (Alterations and extensions) of the Islington Unitary Development Plan 2002; objectives in the Core Strategy Submission Document June 2010 and Islington's Urban Design Guide 2006."
